WEBVTT

00:00:06.208 --> 00:00:09.760
♪Holding hands silently
as flowers fall and winds rise♪

00:00:10.432 --> 00:00:13.536
♪Dark tresses cascade like mountains.
Dreams intertwine♪

00:00:13.536 --> 00:00:17.856
♪Painting realms, clouds in palm,
my brushwork for you♪

00:00:18.048 --> 00:00:22.112
♪Light and shadow overlap
my name across time and space♪

00:00:22.272 --> 00:00:25.960
♪Across starry rivers,
I chase dreams afar♪

00:00:26.400 --> 00:00:30.624
♪Arms spread wide,
falling through heaven and earth♪

00:00:30.760 --> 00:00:33.280
♪The rhythm of breath and heartbeat♪

00:00:33.440 --> 00:00:38.464
♪A meeting of the souls♪

00:00:39.168 --> 00:00:43.424
♪Through shifting seas and lands,
I'd know you still♪

00:00:43.840 --> 00:00:47.800
♪Eyes bright as moonlit skies,
untouched by worldly dust♪

00:00:48.032 --> 00:00:51.680
♪Smiling gazes write eternity♪

00:00:51.680 --> 00:00:56.768
=The Crush=

00:00:57.235 --> 00:00:59.721
=Episode 22=
(Turning the Tide, Truth Revealed)

00:01:00.108 --> 00:01:00.960
(Gu's Tea House)

00:01:00.960 --> 00:01:01.640
Miss Niaoniao,

00:01:01.840 --> 00:01:02.640
our business

00:01:02.720 --> 00:01:04.400
has always been with Li's Tea Estate.

00:01:04.840 --> 00:01:05.640
Why

00:01:05.840 --> 00:01:07.400
is the contract with Li's Tea Estate

00:01:07.600 --> 00:01:09.440
being signed with Gu's Tea Estate now?

00:01:10.080 --> 00:01:10.760
Mr. Li,

00:01:11.400 --> 00:01:13.080
now that I'm part of the Li family,

00:01:13.480 --> 00:01:15.560
there's no distinction
between Gu's Tea Estate

00:01:15.560 --> 00:01:16.520
and Li's Tea Estate.

00:01:17.520 --> 00:01:18.560
For the new contract,

00:01:18.640 --> 00:01:19.640
I'll offer both of you

00:01:19.720 --> 00:01:20.760
another percent discount.

00:01:21.480 --> 00:01:22.560
What do you think?

00:01:25.840 --> 00:01:27.400
Since you said that,

00:01:27.960 --> 00:01:28.720
we'll entrust

00:01:28.840 --> 00:01:31.440
our business
to Gu's Tea Estate from now on.

00:01:31.840 --> 00:01:32.840
We'll rely on

00:01:33.000 --> 00:01:33.920
your generous support.

00:01:35.280 --> 00:01:35.880
Hold it!

00:01:36.680 --> 00:01:37.640
Let me see

00:01:37.960 --> 00:01:39.560
who's using Li's Tea Estate

00:01:39.840 --> 00:01:41.240
to swindle people here!

00:01:42.920 --> 00:01:44.800
Madam, why have you come?

00:01:45.520 --> 00:01:46.720
If I hadn't come,

00:01:47.080 --> 00:01:49.760
you'd have hollowed out
Li's Tea Estate completely!

00:01:50.400 --> 00:01:52.040
When did Li's Tea Estate's business

00:01:52.120 --> 00:01:54.080
get transferred to Gu's Tea Estate?

00:01:54.720 --> 00:01:55.920
You're not worthy

00:01:56.400 --> 00:01:57.480
to stamp our seal!

00:01:58.640 --> 00:02:01.240
Madam, what are you talking about?

00:02:02.000 --> 00:02:04.120
Now that I'm married into the Li family,

00:02:04.120 --> 00:02:06.600
there's no separation
between Li's Tea Estate

00:02:06.840 --> 00:02:08.400
and Gu's Tea Estate.

00:02:09.280 --> 00:02:11.040
A mere concubine

00:02:11.280 --> 00:02:12.512
has no right

00:02:12.720 --> 00:02:15.000
to represent Li's Tea Estate publicly.

00:02:15.200 --> 00:02:16.360
Our business

00:02:16.720 --> 00:02:18.160
isn't yours to manage!

00:02:20.680 --> 00:02:23.760
You two have been our longtime partners.

00:02:23.920 --> 00:02:25.920
How could you humor
this concubine's antics?

00:02:26.680 --> 00:02:28.240
Out of our past relationship,

00:02:28.640 --> 00:02:30.560
I'll let this slide.

00:02:31.400 --> 00:02:32.400
You two may leave now.

00:02:40.400 --> 00:02:42.720
Can't you distinguish your real friend?

00:02:46.160 --> 00:02:46.960
Madam,

00:02:47.960 --> 00:02:49.480
outside the Li Manor,

00:02:50.040 --> 00:02:51.840
your tantrums and unreasonable demands

00:02:51.840 --> 00:02:53.360
won't be tolerated.

00:02:54.320 --> 00:02:55.400
Business is just business.

00:02:56.120 --> 00:02:58.840
These two owners want
my written commitment.

00:02:59.080 --> 00:03:00.440
After all,

00:03:01.560 --> 00:03:02.560
who would refuse profits?

00:03:04.320 --> 00:03:06.760
Even if Zixuan
isn't managing affairs now,

00:03:07.160 --> 00:03:09.440
don't think you can deceive everyone.

00:03:09.960 --> 00:03:11.000
If this goes to court,

00:03:11.400 --> 00:03:14.080
you might spend the rest
of your life in prison!

00:03:14.560 --> 00:03:16.080
If we actually go to court,

00:03:17.120 --> 00:03:19.080
all our past dealings

00:03:19.160 --> 00:03:20.600
will come to light.

00:03:22.480 --> 00:03:23.720
I can manage,

00:03:24.240 --> 00:03:26.080
but if you go to prison,

00:03:26.360 --> 00:03:28.880
what will happen to Young Master Zimo?

00:03:29.720 --> 00:03:30.360
You...

00:03:31.960 --> 00:03:33.280
You vicious woman!

00:03:33.760 --> 00:03:35.280
Don't push things too far.

00:03:37.960 --> 00:03:39.560
The tea estate's business

00:03:39.840 --> 00:03:42.160
will have nothing to do
with your family from now on.

00:03:43.120 --> 00:03:43.680
Oh,

00:03:44.000 --> 00:03:45.080
I forgot to remind you.

00:03:46.040 --> 00:03:47.560
Losing this business

00:03:47.560 --> 00:03:49.840
cuts off the cash flow.

00:03:50.720 --> 00:03:52.560
The workers' wages

00:03:52.840 --> 00:03:55.680
and Young Master Zimo's tavern debts

00:03:55.760 --> 00:03:57.000
will become unpaid.

00:03:57.560 --> 00:03:58.560
You should hurry back

00:03:58.560 --> 00:04:00.720
and sell off your valuables

00:04:00.720 --> 00:04:03.080
before outsiders strip the manor bare

00:04:03.280 --> 00:04:05.040
and leave you homeless.

00:04:05.160 --> 00:04:05.760
You...

00:04:10.800 --> 00:04:11.800
What a lively scene!

00:04:16.920 --> 00:04:17.600
Miss Gu.

00:04:18.480 --> 00:04:20.160
You didn't inform us about

00:04:20.280 --> 00:04:22.400
such a grand opening ceremony?

00:04:27.840 --> 00:04:28.960
Haven't you noticed

00:04:29.680 --> 00:04:31.160
something suspicious about Niaoniao?

00:04:31.200 --> 00:04:33.720
Given my tea skills,

00:04:33.720 --> 00:04:35.720
could I replace Mr. Zixuan
in the competition?

00:04:36.680 --> 00:04:38.960
From overthrowing Mr. Wang
of Tianxiang Tea House

00:04:39.320 --> 00:04:40.440
to revealing herself

00:04:41.200 --> 00:04:42.720
as your savior...

00:04:43.000 --> 00:04:44.880
I wore white clothes and tied up my hair

00:04:44.880 --> 00:04:46.240
for better mobility.

00:04:46.640 --> 00:04:50.160
Now, she's brought back
to the manor by your mother.

00:04:50.920 --> 00:04:53.120
When connecting all these events,

00:04:54.000 --> 00:04:55.160
it appears

00:04:55.400 --> 00:04:57.320
Niaoniao was taken advantage
of by your mother.

00:04:57.760 --> 00:04:58.840
But actually,

00:04:59.520 --> 00:05:00.680
I think

00:05:01.080 --> 00:05:02.520
your mother

00:05:02.520 --> 00:05:04.160
is a pawn used by Niaoniao.

00:05:08.480 --> 00:05:10.600
But what's her purpose in doing this?

00:05:14.480 --> 00:05:16.400
I haven't figured that out yet.

00:05:17.760 --> 00:05:19.160
But I do have a plan.

00:05:21.560 --> 00:05:22.760
Will you trust me?

00:05:23.600 --> 00:05:25.440
I'll come to see you again tomorrow.

00:05:40.384 --> 00:05:44.576
(Gu's Tea House)

00:05:47.960 --> 00:05:48.800
You two,

00:05:51.120 --> 00:05:53.120
today's matter is our family affair.

00:05:53.120 --> 00:05:54.080
Nothing to do with you.

00:05:55.280 --> 00:05:56.480
Miss Niaoniao forged the seal

00:05:57.120 --> 00:05:58.240
and imitated my handwriting.

00:05:58.920 --> 00:06:00.480
Tomorrow, I'll report it to officials.

00:06:01.000 --> 00:06:02.320
By then, your contract

00:06:02.360 --> 00:06:03.560
will naturally become invalid.

00:06:04.280 --> 00:06:05.400
But don't worry.

00:06:06.080 --> 00:06:07.120
Our business with you

00:06:07.120 --> 00:06:08.200
- Are you okay?
- won't change.

00:06:08.400 --> 00:06:10.360
You two may leave for today.

00:06:11.000 --> 00:06:11.560
We're leaving.

00:06:14.240 --> 00:06:15.200
Miss Niaoniao,

00:06:15.920 --> 00:06:17.240
from the very beginning,

00:06:17.440 --> 00:06:18.400
I've been suspicious

00:06:18.680 --> 00:06:20.680
that you weren't Zixuan's savior.

00:06:21.080 --> 00:06:24.280
Now, I should address you as Gu Nianyao.

00:06:27.600 --> 00:06:28.680
The Gu family of Jiangnan.

00:06:29.280 --> 00:06:30.360
Gu's Tea Estate.

00:06:30.880 --> 00:06:31.920
Am I right?

00:06:32.440 --> 00:06:33.560
What did you call her?

00:06:36.080 --> 00:06:36.640
Miss Gu.

00:06:37.560 --> 00:06:39.600
You came
for your family incident, right?

00:06:41.720 --> 00:06:42.400
My father told me

00:06:42.400 --> 00:06:43.560
about it.

00:06:44.000 --> 00:06:45.680
It had weighed on his conscience.

00:06:46.280 --> 00:06:48.400
Your tea emphasized
a lingering aroma in the bowl.

00:06:48.560 --> 00:06:49.640
But storing tea too long

00:06:50.040 --> 00:06:51.240
would allow fungi to grow.

00:06:52.240 --> 00:06:53.360
Though the amount was small,

00:06:53.360 --> 00:06:55.440
it wasn't the cause
of the illness in the court.

00:06:56.000 --> 00:06:57.120
My father hesitated

00:06:57.320 --> 00:06:58.760
about whether to report it.

00:06:59.720 --> 00:07:01.480
Considering your tea business's scale,

00:07:01.680 --> 00:07:03.160
if it wasn't clarified,

00:07:03.320 --> 00:07:04.440
problems would arise later.

00:07:05.000 --> 00:07:06.480
So my father reported truthfully,

00:07:06.480 --> 00:07:07.360
but he emphasized

00:07:08.160 --> 00:07:09.920
the small amount couldn't cause illness.

00:07:10.600 --> 00:07:11.720
But unexpectedly,

00:07:12.480 --> 00:07:13.200
the imperial court

00:07:13.760 --> 00:07:15.160
still shut down your business.

00:07:16.480 --> 00:07:17.720
After my father returned,

00:07:17.720 --> 00:07:18.680
he fell gravely ill.

00:07:19.280 --> 00:07:20.840
But he still had someone

00:07:20.840 --> 00:07:22.000
send you

00:07:22.240 --> 00:07:23.480
all the money he could spare

00:07:23.560 --> 00:07:24.880
to ensure your livelihood.

00:07:27.080 --> 00:07:27.760
Li Zixuan,

00:07:28.480 --> 00:07:29.560
even now,

00:07:29.560 --> 00:07:31.080
you still pretend to be righteous?

00:07:31.520 --> 00:07:33.560
If you'd truly helped
us in crisis back then

00:07:33.560 --> 00:07:34.520
by sending the money,

00:07:34.920 --> 00:07:36.720
how could my family have been destroyed?

00:07:38.440 --> 00:07:40.560
Now that I'm in your hands,

00:07:40.960 --> 00:07:41.720
I've lost.

00:07:42.000 --> 00:07:42.560
I admit it.

00:07:43.880 --> 00:07:44.560
But

00:07:44.800 --> 00:07:47.160
save your hypocritical speeches.

00:07:48.200 --> 00:07:50.920
Even as a ghost, I will

00:07:51.040 --> 00:07:53.400
forever remember your family.

00:08:28.760 --> 00:08:29.560
Miss Gu.

00:08:31.280 --> 00:08:32.080
Miss.

00:08:32.920 --> 00:08:33.680
This is

00:08:33.960 --> 00:08:35.880
all my jewelry.

00:08:36.080 --> 00:08:37.520
I couldn't convert them to cash.

00:08:37.920 --> 00:08:39.040
Please take it.

00:08:39.440 --> 00:08:40.280
Leave quickly.

00:08:40.520 --> 00:08:41.640
Get out of Haiqing.

00:08:44.000 --> 00:08:45.200
What's the meaning of this?

00:08:46.600 --> 00:08:48.720
They'll send you to the yamen tomorrow.

00:08:49.280 --> 00:08:51.080
I brought you here.

00:08:51.680 --> 00:08:53.000
If this goes to court,

00:08:53.720 --> 00:08:54.800
many matters

00:08:55.320 --> 00:08:56.720
will implicate me.

00:08:58.400 --> 00:08:59.840
You want me to leave,

00:09:01.000 --> 00:09:02.560
but in this vast world,

00:09:04.280 --> 00:09:06.360
where can I find refuge?

00:09:07.920 --> 00:09:09.680
I'm already homeless.

00:09:11.320 --> 00:09:13.080
Even if I face the officials tomorrow,

00:09:13.840 --> 00:09:15.760
I'll fight to the bitter end.

00:09:17.000 --> 00:09:19.920
You people framed my family back then.

00:09:20.920 --> 00:09:21.520
Tomorrow,

00:09:21.520 --> 00:09:23.840
I'll return every deed

00:09:24.120 --> 00:09:25.560
to you in full.

00:09:27.160 --> 00:09:28.560
Your hatred for the Li family

00:09:29.440 --> 00:09:31.280
truly can't be let go of?

00:09:36.080 --> 00:09:37.680
A ten-year-old girl

00:09:38.960 --> 00:09:41.400
watched her entire family perish.

00:09:42.960 --> 00:09:45.080
She can survive alone by pleasing men.

00:09:46.400 --> 00:09:47.360
Tell me,

00:09:48.000 --> 00:09:49.400
dozens of our family lives,

00:09:50.720 --> 00:09:52.040
who will atone for them?

00:10:02.560 --> 00:10:03.920
Let your hatred for the Li family

00:10:05.400 --> 00:10:07.200
all fall upon me.

00:10:10.400 --> 00:10:11.680
What do you mean by this?

00:10:14.480 --> 00:10:16.800
I'm the one who failed your family.

00:10:18.720 --> 00:10:19.720
Back then, Master Li

00:10:20.360 --> 00:10:22.360
truly exhausted all our family's wealth

00:10:22.360 --> 00:10:23.720
to send aid to your family.

00:10:24.360 --> 00:10:25.560
But at that time,

00:10:25.960 --> 00:10:28.040
I had just conceived Zimo.

00:10:28.280 --> 00:10:29.960
If the Li family had collapsed,

00:10:30.120 --> 00:10:31.560
what would have become of Zimo?

00:10:32.560 --> 00:10:33.320
I

00:10:34.120 --> 00:10:35.280
secretly intercepted

00:10:35.840 --> 00:10:37.040
that money

00:10:37.720 --> 00:10:40.600
and returned it to our accounts

00:10:40.920 --> 00:10:42.280
while Master Li was gravely ill.

00:10:42.920 --> 00:10:45.080
All of this was my doing.

00:10:45.440 --> 00:10:46.840
Direct your hatred for the Li family

00:10:47.520 --> 00:10:48.840
all at me.

00:10:51.840 --> 00:10:52.760
Do you think

00:10:55.160 --> 00:10:56.720
I'll show mercy?

00:10:59.640 --> 00:11:00.680
I only hope

00:11:01.680 --> 00:11:04.160
that after avenging your hatred,

00:11:05.720 --> 00:11:07.440
you can start anew

00:11:07.960 --> 00:11:10.280
and live an ordinary life.

00:11:11.920 --> 00:11:13.320
- Miss Gu!
- Miss Gu!